    - target: {fileID: 4573627944131785250, guid: 8870a2dbc1e150b45949c75107370e0d, type: 3}
      propertyPath: fullText
      value: '<b>NOTICE</b>


        In case of thermal hallucinations during Anamnesis
        sessions, do not attempt to leave the designated ''safe zone''. The heat
        is a synaptic response, not a physical threat. Termination of the session
        without proper de-synchronization may lead to permanent ego death'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 4573627944131785250, guid: 8870a2dbc1e150b45949c75107370e0d, type: 3}
